owl:Ontology.terms:description: This ontology introduces the definition of a set of bicycle parking facilities related terms. It reuses and extends the MobiVoc (see http://schema.mobivoc.org/) and the schema.org (see https://schema.org) vocabularies.
owl:Ontology.rdfs:label: Open Velopark Vocabulary

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Place close to another place.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: close to

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Relates the civic structure to its capacity.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has capacity
hat Kapazität

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates that a price specification is due for a certain time specification.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: due for time
fällig für Zeitdauer

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the entrance of a parking facility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: entrance
hat Einfahrt

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the exit of a parking facility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: exit
hat Ausfahrt

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The operator of a civic structure or facility. Operator and owner can be different business entitites.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: betrieben von
operated by

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The owner of a civic structure or facility. Owner and operator can be different business entities.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: in Besitz von
owned by

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Physical address of the item.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: address

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An amenity feature (e.g. a characteristic or service) of a place or accomodation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: amenity feature

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A contact point for a person or organization.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: contact point

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The day of the week for which certain opening hours are valid.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: day of week

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The geo coordinates of a place.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: geo

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A URL to a map of the place.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has map

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The hours during which a service or contact is available.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: hours available

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The WebSite or SoftwareApplication where the interactions took place.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: interaction service

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The hours during which a service or contact is available.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: opening hours

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A photograph of this place.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: photo

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: One or more detailed price specifications, indicating the unit price and delivery or payment charges.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: price specification

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates a type of bicycle that is allowed in a certain parking facility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: allows

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the specific type of bicycle that is allowed in a certain parking facility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: bicycle type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The owner of the data about a certain bicycle parking facility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: data owner

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The date of the given real-time capacity.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: date

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: identifier

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the current value of the real-time capacity.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: current value

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates that the usage of the civic structure is for free.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: free of charge
kostenlos

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the total number of levels a parking facility has.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Anzahl Ebenen
number of levels

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates that a time period overnight is possible.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: overnight
über Nacht

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the end value of a time period.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Endzeit
time end value

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the start value of a time period.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Anfangszeit
time start value

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the time unit a value is specified for.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Zeiteinheit
time unit

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the total number of parking spaces of a parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Gesamtkapazität
total capacity

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A language someone may use with or at the item, service or place. Please use one of the language codes from the IETF BCP 47 standard.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: available language

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The closing hour of the place or service on the given day(s) of the week.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: closes

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A person or organization can have different contact points, for different purposes. For example, a sales contact point, a PR contact point and so on. This property is used to specify the kind of contact point.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: contact type

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Email address.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: email

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The name of an item.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: name

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The opening hour of the place or service on the given day(s) of the week.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: opens

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The offer price of a product, or of a price component when attached to PriceSpecification and its subtypes.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: price

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The currency of the price. Use standard formats: ISO 4217 currency format (e.g. USD).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: price

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A flag to signal that a Place is open to public visitors.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: public access

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A telephone number.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: telephone

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the maximum amount of bicycle of a certain type that are allowed in a parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: bicylces amount

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates whether a certain type of allowed bicycle has a counting system or not, for a given parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: counting system

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The final closing date of a parking facility (in ISO 8601 date format).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: end date

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the type of audience that can make use of a certain parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: intended audience

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the maximum amount of time that bicycles are allowed to be parked in a certain parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: maximum storage time

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the minimum amount of time that bicycles are allowed to be parked in a certain parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: minimun storage time

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Description of how parking facility users must proceed when their bicycles are removed.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: post removal action

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Description of the conditions under which a bicycle may be removed from a certain parking facility.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: removal conditions

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the operational restrictions that a certain parking facility may have.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: restrictions

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The initial opening date of a parking facility (in ISO 8601 date format).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: start date

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An instance of this class represents the legal agent making (or seeking) a particular offering. This can be a legal body or a person. A business entity has at least a primary mailing address and contact details. For this, typical address standards (vCard) and location data (geo, WGS84) can be attached. Note that the location of the business entity is not necessarily the location from which the product or service is being available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Business Entity
Juristische Person

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Building or structure designed for use as a bicycle parking facility.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Bicycle Parking Station
Fahrradparkstation

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Capacity of a civic structure.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Capacity
Kapazität

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Any facility or area assigned for parking vehicles. A parking facility can provide one or more parking spaces.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Parkeinrichtung
Parking Facility

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Entrance of a parking facility where vehicles can enter.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Einfahrt
Entrance

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Exit of a parking facility where vehicles can leave.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Ausfahrt
Exit

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Real-time capacity of a civic structure.
Real-time capacity of a parking facility or parking space.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Echtzeit Kapazität
Real Time Capacity

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Specific time a price specification is due for.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Time specification
Zeitspezifikation

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A public structure, such as a town hall or concert hall, parking facility or charging point.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Civic Structure
Zivile Struktur

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A contact point for customer service.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Contact Point

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The day of the week, e.g. used to specify to which day the opening hours of an OpeningHoursSpecification refer.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Day of Week

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The geographic coordinates of a place or event.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Geo Coordinates

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The geographic shape of a place. A GeoShape can be described using several properties whose values are based on latitude/longitude pairs.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Geo Shape

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Specifies a location feature by providing a structured value representing a feature of an accommodation as a property-value pair of varying degrees of formality.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: LocationFeatureSpecification

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A map.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Map

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A structured value providing information about the opening hours of a place or a certain service inside a place.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Opening Hours Specification

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A photograph.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Photograph

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Place

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The mailing address.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Postal Address

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A structured value representing a price or price range for an item.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Preisspezifikation
Price specification

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A vehicle is a device that is designed or used to transport people or cargo over land, water, air, or through space.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Fahrzeug
Vehicle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A WebSite is a set of related web pages and other items typically served from a single web domain and accessible via URLs.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: WebSite

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A bicycle that is allowed in a given parking facility.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Allowed Bicycle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Covered and lockable bicycle parking facility on public roads.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Bicycle Case

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a bicycle pump available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Bicycle Pump

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a bicycle rental service available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Bike Rental Service

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has surveillance cameras available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Camera Surveillance

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A bicycle specially adapted to transport load.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cargo Bicycle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has an electrical bicycle charging point available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Charging Point

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An electrically powered bicycle.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Electric Bicycle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has an electronic access system.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Electronic Access

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a locker service available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Locker Service

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a bicycle maintenance service available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Maintenance Service

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Bicycle parking facility for residents of a given neighborhood.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Neighborhood Parking Facility

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has personnel supervision available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Personnel Supervision

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A regular bicycle that does not have any special features.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Regular Bicycle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A bicycle designed to be ridden by more than one person.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Tandem Bicycle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a toilet service available.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Toilet Service

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A human-or electric powered, pedal-driven, single-track vehicle, having two wheels attached to a frame, one behind the other.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Bicycle
Fahrrad
Vélo
